###################################
#                                 #
#  TriMines (v. 1.3.0 [4/13/06])  #
#                                 #
###################################

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:

	- SDL (www.libsdl.org)
	- Linux/Unix-Based OS or Windows.

COMPILE:

$ ./build

RUN:

$ ./trimines

______________________________________________________________________________________________
MOUSE & KEYBOARD:

LEFT CLICK: 		- uncover triangle.
RIGHT CLICK: 		- mark as mine or uncertain.
MIDDLE CLICK:		- clear the surrounding triangles if the right number of triangles is already
			  flagged.
WHEEL UP/DOWN:	 	- choose amount of mines. (enabled only at start when the mouse pointer is on
			  the smiley bar).
F1:			- Solve the game.
ESCAPE:			- Back to menu (or quit game if already in the menu).
